      "content": "That's a good start. I want to make sure the post doesn't sound one-sided though. Can you also help me frame the counter-arguments from the perspective of people who believe regulation is necessary for public safety or preventing misinformation? I want to see how they would try to debunk the Mill/libertarian angle.",
